#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Skills** Perception +3, Stealth +6    \n"
"**Senses** passive Perception 13    \n"
"**Languages** --    \n"
"**Challenge** 2 (450 XP) \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/saber_toothed_tiger.md:23
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Keen Smell.** The tiger has advantage on Wisdom (Perception) checks that "
"rely on smell.    \n"
"**Pounce.** If the tiger moves at least 20 feet straight toward a creature "
"and then hits it with a claw attack on the same turn, that target must "
"succeed on a DC 14 Strength saving throw or be knocked prone. If the target "
"is prone, the tiger can make one bite attack against it as a bonus "
"action. \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/saber_toothed_tiger.md:26
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"### Actions    \n"
"**Bite.** _Melee Weapon Attack:_ +6 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. _Hit:_ "
"10 (1d10 + 5) piercing damage.    \n"
"**Claw.** _Melee Weapon Attack:_ +6 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. _Hit:_ "
"12 (2d6 + 5) slashing damage. \n"
msgstr ""
